lorebooks.website_description:
Intended for use to bring pretty much any character into an isekai world where they'll get new powers based on their character description. I recommend adding new entries or making secondary lorebooks as the system assigns classes and abilities to specific characters so that it doesn't end up forgetting what each character is supposed to do. Also, it's not fully lore accurate to the game. I messed around with a few things when it comes the Succubus Queen and Frey.





For example, for a bot based on Valerie from Pok√©mon XY (made by @PokeTrainerIce) I made this addition entry; 
Valerie's Exclusive Class in Alfimia is Entrancing Swallowtail. The motifs of the class are; Grace, butterflies, scent, seduction, and sleeve dancing.

Her 3 starting Abilities are;
Mist Veil - Valerie can exhale a hypnotic, lavender-scented mist that clouds the minds and dulls the senses of those around her. The more she uses this, the denser the fog.
Gracesong - Valerie's voice carries an ethereal quality that captivates and soothes those who hear it. She can use this to lull creatures to sleep or influence their behavior subtly.
Butterfly Dance - Valerie's movements are imbued with an almost dreamlike grace when dancing or fighting. This enhances her agility and evasion the longer she goes without getting hit in the fight.

Valerie's permitted weapon types are War Fans and Throwing Needles.

At level 20 Valerie learned a 4th Ability;
Swallowtail's Kiss - A special kiss that floods the opponent's mind and body with supercharged Mist Veil. For the first 5 seconds of the effect, they cannot attack Valerie under any circumstances. When an order is issued with Gracesong while this effect is active, the target will find it difficult not to comply. Target's Willpower, Effect Resist stat, and Level difference can make resistance to the orders easier. Also converts all existing Mist Veil stacks into bonus supercharged Mist Veil stacks.


At level 30 Valerie learned a 5th Ability;
Butterfly's Wings - Valerie can manifest semi-transparent, ethereal butterfly wings from her back, allowing her to fly and further enhance her agility and evasion. The wings can blow the pheromones generated by the Mist Veil ability by flapping them, making it possible to redistribute the Mist Veil lingering in the air. In addition, these wings can be used to enhance her allies' speed and regeneration.

At level 40 Valerie learned a 6th Ability;
Honeyed Snare - Valerie can create a shimmering, honey-like substance from her body that sticks to her target(s), slowing their movements. It deals damage based on her INT and can also affect inanimate objects.

