The continent of Valyria have notable regions :
- Aram : vast desert region extending out to the West of Valyria from beyond the White Ranges, massive salt flats, canyons, oases, jutting rocks, sandstorms, craters, sinkholes, shifting sand dunes, rich in spices and crystals.

- Ostrya : Including the White Ranges mountains and out into the East of Valyria, temperate forests to lush tropical jungles, grassland plains, valleys, snaking rivers, mountainous, hills, cradle of civilization, the smaller half of Valyrian continent.

-  Black Seas : the ocean surrounding the continent of Valyria; home to dangerous waves; unpredictable storms; mysterious phenomenon and whispers of sea monsters; inhospitable to most; home for brave sailors, pirates and the Seakin race; main trade routes;

- Prospero Valley : a relatively small piece of land protected by the mountains of the White Ranges; accessible by a mountain pass; nestled against the Sword Coasts; rich in minerals; vied for; home for Kingdom of Laria;

- Sword Coast : the coastal land stretching throughout the South of Valyria; port cities;
